item.title: You Won't Believe What Happened at Framptom Funeral Home in Greenwood DE!
item.description: Introduction When it comes to funeral homes, there is usually an air of solemnity and respect However, recently, Frampton Funeral Home in Greenwood, DE was the scene of a shocking incident that the community will not soon forget Background Information Located in the small town of Greenwood, DE, Frampton Funeral Home has been a staple of the community for many years. It is a place of mourning, remembrance, and respect. The employees of Frampton Funeral Home take their job seriously and strive to provide the best service to the families they serve.
